<section class="section section--compact" id="new-york-in-brief">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="in-brief">
      <p class="in-brief__text" id="new-york-in-brief-text">TechBrot serves New York businesses remotely with the same standard everywhere in the state: a named operator, weekly reconcile cadence, and pricing in writing before work begins.</p>
      <p class="in-brief__source">Independent · not a directory — the operators are ours</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--compact section--tier-hub" id="new-york-tldr">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tldr">
      <p class="tldr__label">TL;DR</p>
      <p class="tldr__body" id="new-york-tldr-body">New York businesses don't need a bookkeeper nearby — they need one who closes on time. We work your file remotely, reconcile weekly, and pick up the phone during your business hours.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--compact" id="new-york-ai-summary">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="ai-summary ai-summary--ruled">
      <div class="ai-summary__item"><p class="ai-summary__question">Does TechBrot have an office in New York?</p><p class="ai-summary__answer">We serve New York remotely with named operators working your business hours — no office visit required, none offered.</p></div>
      <div class="ai-summary__item"><p class="ai-summary__question">Can you handle New York sales tax?</p><p class="ai-summary__answer">Yes — state and local filings are part of monthly engagements for New York clients.</p></div>
      <div class="ai-summary__item"><p class="ai-summary__question">What does bookkeeping cost in New York?</p><p class="ai-summary__answer">The same as everywhere we work: fixed fee, written scope, priced from the free file review.</p></div>
      <div class="ai-summary__item"><p class="ai-summary__question">Do you work with NYC businesses specifically?</p><p class="ai-summary__answer">Yes — retail, restaurants, agencies, and professional firms across the five boroughs and the rest of the state.</p></div>
      <div class="ai-summary__item"><p class="ai-summary__question">How fast can you start?</p><p class="ai-summary__answer">The file review takes three business days from accountant access; most engagements start the week after.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="new-york-form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap:var(--space-12);align-items:start">
      <div>
        <p class="section__eyebrow">New York intake</p>
        <h2 class="section__heading">Tell us where the books hurt.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--text-body);max-width:30em">A New York-assigned ProAdvisor replies within one business day.</p>
        <div class="trust-row" style="margin-top:var(--space-8);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space-5)">
          <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value">Your hours</p><p class="trust-row__label">Operators work ET for New York clients</p></div>
          <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value">Fixed-fee, written scope</p><p class="trust-row__label">Pricing before work begins</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <form class="intake-form" action="#" method="post">
        <div class="intake-grid">
          <div class="intake-field"><label class="intake-field__label" for="ny-name">Name</label><input id="ny-name" name="name" type="text" required></div>
          <div class="intake-field"><label class="intake-field__label" for="ny-email">Email</label><input id="ny-email" name="email" type="email" required></div>
          <div class="intake-field"><label class="intake-field__label" for="ny-company">Company</label><input id="ny-company" name="company" type="text" required></div>
          <div class="intake-field"><label class="intake-field__label" for="ny-city">City</label><input id="ny-city" name="city" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Brooklyn"></div>
          <div class="intake-field"><label class="intake-field__label" for="ny-platform">Platform</label><select id="ny-platform" name="platform"><option>QuickBooks Online</option><option>QuickBooks Desktop</option><option>Other / not sure</option></select></div>
          <div class="intake-field"><label class="intake-field__label" for="ny-urgency">Urgency</label><select id="ny-urgency" name="urgency"><option>This week</option><option>This month</option><option>Just researching</option></select></div>
        </div>
        <div class="intake-consent">
          <label class="intake-checkbox"><input type="checkbox" name="consent" value="agreed" required><span>I agree to be contacted about my inquiry.</span></label>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="intent" value="new-york"><input type="hidden" name="state" value="new-york"><input type="hidden" name="source_page" value="/find-an-accountant/new-york/"><input type="hidden" name="source_type" value="state-pillar"><input type="hidden" name="funnel_stage" value="MOFU"><input type="hidden" name="operator_candidate" value="false">
        <div>
          <button class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" type="submit">Book the Discovery Call</button>
          <p class="intake-form__reassurance">No spam, no list, no obligation.</p>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
